    "Id": "vehicledef_HUNTER",
    "Name": "Hunter Light Support Tank",
    "UIName": "Hunter Light Support Tank (Standard)",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Hunter Light Support Tank</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Standard </color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Inner Sphere</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>5/8 (Tracked)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>175 Fusion</color></b>\n\nThe Hunter Light Support Tank, popular among planetary militias and second-line units, is a cheap, reliable, and effective combat vehicle designed by Defiance Industries to provide covering fire support for withdrawing combat units from the front lines.\n\nIts low profile and twenty-tube LRM launcher allow the Hunter to exploit sheltering terrain and provide indirect fire support for prolonged periods, thanks to its two tons of ammunition. The rear-facing Flamer provides anti-infantry defense in case of emergencies, but is more commonly used to cover retreating units rather than engage in direct combat.",
